OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A whistleblower who helped expose      
OL,6, allegations of Australian war crimes in
OL,7, Afghanistan has pleaded guilty to      
OL,8, leaking classified information.        
OL,10,FDavid McBride was due to face trial    
OL,11,Fnext week, but changed his plea after a
OL,12,Flegal ruling scuppered his defence.    
OL,14,FMcBride - an ex-military lawyer - said 
OL,15,Fhe felt a moral duty to speak up after 
OL,16,Fhis internal complaints were ignored.  
OL,18,FA landmark inquiry later found evidence
OL,19,Fthat Australian forces had unlawfully  
OL,20,Fkilled 39 Afghans during the war.      
